      m_Calls: []
  m_text: This enemy wanders freely until a trail point enters its detection radius.
    Once it detects a nearby point, it switches into chase mode and begins following
    the trail. Unlike the standard mode, it does not destroy points it reaches. Instead,
    it remembers which points it has already visited and prefers moving toward the
    closest trail point with the fewest visits, avoiding going straight back to the
    point it came from unless there are no other options. When it eventually reaches
    the end of the trail, it naturally reverses direction and follows the trail back
    the other way. If no trail points are in range, the enemy returns to wandering.
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
